---
title: Chicken and Squash Korma Style Curry with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Basmati Rice
description: A comforting and mildly spiced Indian favourite, korma sauce pairs well with any kind of veg or protein. Here, this veg-filled version heroes chicken, butternut squash and Tenderstem® for a colourful meal.
